item.title: Biden Admin Orders Release of Migrants Into US Despite Ban
item.description: Two days after issuing an executive order it framed as a tough crackdown on illegal immigration, the Biden administration instructed border agents in southwestern California to release migrants from 94 of 100 countries in the Eastern Hemisphere into the United States.
